title: All About History Book of Kings & Queens - 2014  UK
description:
All About History Book of Kings & Queens - 2014  UK

180 Pages | True PDF | English | 24 MB 


Take a look at some of the most iconic and influential monarchs the world has ever seen, from Herod and Cleopatra to Henry VIII and Louis XIV. Find out more about the 30 kings and queens who changed the world, the ten kings who can lay claim to the bloodiest reign, the royal warriors who did battle to claim their thrones, and how the British monarchy was born.
